OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright or sunny spells at
OL,6,Ffirst, but generally a cloudy day with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, with the odd
OL,8,Fheavier burst possible. Occasionally
OL,9,Ffresh southerly or southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly cloudy with further
OL,12,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain,
OL,13,Fhowever Orkney becomes dry towards the
OL,14,Fend of the night and the cloud breaks
OL,15,Fup. Occasionally fresh westerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
